{"tid":1229591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日等緊朋友嗰陣，叫晒佢哋即時登記做選民！！！之後再確認佢哋真係有登記到！！","createTime":"2019-06-16T03:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T17:07:51.000Z","uid":262428,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d5210002d3b052ea9a253346d7c442100c7cc192","tid":1229591,"uid":262428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:39:42.000Z","msg":"<em>所有人叫晒自己嘅朋友登記做選民！！ <br />\n如果今次你阿爸阿媽有陪你出去，請更加要叫佢哋登記做選民！ </em><br />\n<br />\n官方表格可喺各區民政事務處都有得攞！<br />\n或者上網dowload印出嚟： <a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf  \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2Fform%2FREO-1%28C%29.pdf%20%20&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2Fhs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=3731d8f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/pdf/form/REO-1(C).pdf  </a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">（今日行公園冇Printer或Scanner可以點？<br />\n可以考慮用鍵盤戰線嘅填表工具： <a href=\"https://kbfl-campaign.github.io/ \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkbfl-campaign.github.io%2F%20&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2Fhs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=a6ef08c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://kbfl-campaign.github.io/ </a><br />\n填晒資料會變pdf，方便你即時交表。） </span></span><br />\n<br />\n交表方法： <br />\nemail至form@reo.gov.hk 或者upload去政府個網（網址:<a href=\"http://www.reo-form.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo-form.gov.hk&d=GKwB35BxKisFbiFxv4h%2Fhs0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=f7929192\" target=\"_blank\">www.reo-form.gov.hk</a>） <br />\n（再講一次，冇Scanner可以用上面鍵盤戰線嘅填表工具） <br />\n舊式啲可以寄信（地址：九龍九龍灣展貿徑一號九龍灣國際展貿中心十三樓） <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>登記選民限期得返2個星期！！ </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港後生仔嘅登記率得一半， <br />\n即係話你所有嘅whatsapp group入面， 或者今日同你一齊行喺人，<br />\n起碼有一半人都未登記！！ <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>無論佢講到幾熱血，衝到幾前， <br />\n佢都可能未登記！ </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">求下大家一定要逐個問！ <br />\n逐個確定佢有登記做選民！ </span><br />\n<br />\n求求你！"},{"pid":"dbf416a4d7df9668f9e8595c604e48b6e1778d8d","tid":1229591,"uid":256246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:42:11.000Z","msg":"用github條link就可以直接網上登記？要唔要住址證明果d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b64b189448334ec2153e35f1f91f3f23ed002f8","tid":1229591,"uid":262428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dbf416a4d7df9668f9e8595c604e48b6e1778d8d","tid":1229591,"uid":256246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:42:11.000Z","msg":"用github條link就可以直接網上登記？要唔要住址證明果d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:47:16.000Z","msg":"唔需要<br />\n即填可以直接upload埋"},{"pid":"6c17472ffd9d41a9d1318f067c2d0e87763e8231","tid":1229591,"uid":262428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:50:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f6a34fc6bda834a2759958d39c8d3399f5543c7c","tid":1229591,"uid":262544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"誠心請教，我想問我租住圍村，咁可以點投（投其他屋苑可以嗎，圍村無泛民），今次冷政治感嘅我都要單拖遊行，同想投票"},{"pid":"de617d4af8374080cda410dc1a7ad5bb4fc5bb2b","tid":1229591,"uid":262428,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f6a34fc6bda834a2759958d39c8d3399f5543c7c","tid":1229591,"uid":262544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"誠心請教，我想問我租住圍村，咁可以點投（投其他屋苑可以嗎，圍村無泛民），今次冷政治感嘅我都要單拖遊行，同想投票"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:10:49.000Z","msg":"官方答案：一定唔得，只可以投自己主要居住嘅地點<br />\n但<br />\n(1) 登記咗唔止係區議會，仲有立法會<br />\n(2) 好多支持民主但非泛民嘅組織，都諗緊試吓選傳統嘅保守區，<br />\n可能靠你嘅一票到時係改變結局"},{"pid":"6d94ad7a65eb512eb4f47ac921f56d81306d696a","tid":1229591,"uid":262428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7341152026bc35f2ceda2b60076ea103aaaf37fc","tid":1229591,"uid":137217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5210002d3b052ea9a253346d7c442100c7c